        "2 tablespoons orange juice",
        "3/4 teaspoon grated fresh ginger root",
        "1/4 teaspoon salt",
        "1 teaspoon white sugar",
        "1/4 teaspoon dried orange peel",
        "1 pinch cayenne pepper",
        "1 pinch ground cinnamon"
